snippet.title: Intergalactic Battle Roosters Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2859730/Intergalactic_Battle_Roosters/

It’s time to cluck around and find out. Gear up and pull on the helmets of the Battle Roosters, a hotshot space brigade of poultry with panache. In this quirky, roguelike, bullet hell adventure you’ll combine weapons, upgrades and killer strategies to recover space’s best taco ingredients. Bwark!
